/*
  Cross-Origin headers for ONNX Runtime Web:
  - COOP: same-origin     — required for SharedArrayBuffer (used by WASM threading)
  - COEP: credentialless  — allows the PaddleOCR SDK to load cross-origin
                            subresources (e.g. JS workers) without explicit
                            Cross-Origin-Resource-Policy. Falls back to
                            `require-corp` when the host serves every
                            subresource with its own CORP header.
  - CORP: same-origin     — keeps responses from being embedded by other sites.
*/
Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
Cross-Origin-Embedder-Policy: credentialless
Cross-Origin-Resource-Policy: same-origin
